---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Section from "../components/layout/Section.astro";
import ContactCta from "../components/home/ContactCta.astro";
import { base } from "../lib/url";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Paweł Ryfiak"
  description="Applied Computer Science student at Karel de Grote in Antwerp. Spring Boot, Docker, GitLab CI, and AI-assisted automation. Seeking IT internship or junior backend role."
  path="/about"
>
  <main id="main-content">
    <Section>
      <div class="max-w-3xl" data-reveal>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">About</h1>

        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-base-content/80">
          I am a software engineering student at Karel de Grote Hogeschool in Antwerp,
          focused on backend systems, deployment automation, and practical infrastructure work.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-base-content/70">
          My strongest area is Java and Spring Boot — building REST APIs, validation layers,
          JPA integrations, and running them inside Docker. I have shipped CI/CD pipelines
          on Google Cloud using GitLab CI, Nginx, and Compose-based blue-green deployments.
          Most recently I have been building AI-assisted data extraction tooling with Gemini
          and Spring Boot.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-base-content/70">
          I am expanding into modern frontend work — learning Astro, Svelte, Tailwind CSS,
          and Strapi — by building this portfolio from scratch. Not to become a frontend
          developer, but to understand the full deployment picture.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-base-content/70">
          I am looking for an IT internship or junior backend/automation role where I can
          contribute to a real codebase, learn from experienced engineers, and keep improving
          my DevOps and system design skills. Based in Antwerp, open to remote and EU roles.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href={`${base}projects`} class="btn btn-primary">View projects</a>
          <a href={`${base}blog`} class="btn btn-outline">Read blog</a>
          <!-- Opens the CV language picker rendered by Header -->
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-ghost" data-cv-trigger>Download CV</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <ContactCta />
  </main>
</BaseLayout>








